Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:33.00,CreditInfo,,0,0,0,,\N制作信息\N翻译：AI女孩小雪（https://github.com/SnowAIGirl）\N时间轴：基于 Crunchyroll 官方字幕\N语音识别：faster-whisper（日语→中文直译）\N\N本字幕仅供学习交流，请勿用于商业用途。如侵权请联系删除。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:44.67,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,春天了以为不穿外套\N出来抽根烟也没事。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:47.21,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,但晚上还是挺冷的呢。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:51.30,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,回家之前找个地方抽根烟。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:01:57.72,Default,OHNO,0,0,0,,山田酱，我来接班了。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:01:59.10,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,干杯。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:06.48,DefaultItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,今晚没来啊。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:09.65,DefaultItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,加班？难道要干到天亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:11.94,Default,OHNO,0,0,0,,对了，还有一件事。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:12.82,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:17.03,Default,OHNO,0,0,0,,店长说下班前去一趟。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:26.33,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田山小姐，晚——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:29.21,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(230,1)\bord1.5\fnArial Black\c&H3E31A0&\3c&H2E2763&}pissssssed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:31.71,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(897,1)\an9\bord1.5\fnComic Sans MS\c&H2E251E&\3c&HD6D1D0&\pos(555.5,17)}She's in a foul mood...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:30.92,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哎呀。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:39.39,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,哟，这不是佐佐木先生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:40.43,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嘿。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:43.02,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,别站着，过来坐。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:44.02,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,谢了。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.65,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田山小姐，你——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:53.03,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,你今天休息？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:53.49,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.07,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哦，对，难得休了一天。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:00.41,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,这个回答一听就是血汗工厂。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:09.34,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,休息一天也好。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:28.40,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fs15\fnComic Sans MS\c&HE1E4E3&\frz-6.26\fax0.15\pos(193.5,101)}Cold
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:28.40,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\blur0.3\fs20\fnComic Sans MS\c&HE1E4E3&\frz-5.44\fax0.13\pos(344.5,110.5)}Hot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:28.40,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\blur0.2\fnComic Sans MS\c&HE1E4E3&\frz-5.3\fax0.12\pos(581,128)}Hot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:29.94,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,你不抽烟？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:32.27,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,天冷，去买杯喝的。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:34.40,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,一起吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:39.24,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,心情不好的时候啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:43.95,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,热饮比烟酒更有用哦。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:53.42,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,头一回被人投诉了。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:56.26,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,「我一直觉得她服务态度很好。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:03:59.26,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,但今天闻到她身上有烟味，太失望了」。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:04.31,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,店长让我别在意\N说纯属无理取闹。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.44,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,但遇到这种事啊。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:14.82,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,就觉得一切都好没意思。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.28,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,真可悲。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:28.96,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我不理解为什么一看到\N别人新的一面就觉得被背叛了。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.63,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,都是同一个人啊。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:38.05,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哦，不过我也没资格说别人。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:42.55,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我连你是哪个区的都不知道。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.27,0:04:50.60,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,对、对不起，穿太少出来了\N一直打喷嚏。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:58.86,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田山小姐？你干嘛？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:04.87,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,今晚借你穿。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:13.96,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,好暖和，谢谢你田山小姐。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:29.35,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,不，该我谢你。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.45,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,还有，对不起我得说一句。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.07,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,我不喝咖啡。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:48.41,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,你看起来很惊讶。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:50.54,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不是因为这个。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:53.08,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,其实我也不喝咖啡。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:56.67,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,换别的吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:05:59.25,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,那我要大公牛。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:08.81,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,今天天气真好。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:12.77,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,春天的阳光最治愈了。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.85,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,温暖了我疲惫的身心。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:19.27,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs20\fad(108,103)\fnArial Black\c&H181917&\pos(220,40.5)}I'm so sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:20.57,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs20\fad(108,103)\fnArial Black\c&H181917&\pos(342,63)}I'm so sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.07,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs20\fad(108,103)\fnArial Black\c&H181917&\pos(220,40.5)}I'm so sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:23.57,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs20\fad(108,103)\fnArial Black\c&H181917&\pos(342,63)}I'm so sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:21.32,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,尤其是在被客户骂了之后。
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.19,0:06:21.61,FlashbackTop,SASAKI,0,0,0,,对不起！对不起！
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.61,0:06:23.82,FlashbackTop,SASAKI,0,0,0,,对不起！对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:26.82,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,得回去工作了。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:30.33,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,回去路上顺便去S超市买个午饭。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:35.83,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田山小姐应该是夜班吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:41.13,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,她这个点应该不在……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:47.72,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田山小姐……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:49.97,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:52.47,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,山、山田小姐？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:53.98,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,你好！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:56.69,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你、你怎么在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:59.98,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,等等，你白天也上班？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.90,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,佐佐木先生，冷静点好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.24,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哦，对、对不起。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:10.20,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我基本是夜班但今天替班。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.99,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我来这里是因为……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:14.25,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,冷静……冷静。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:21.13,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,这里是唯一有自动售货机的地方。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:23.38,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哦，这样啊。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:25.51,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,你今天早下班了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:29.01,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不是，我在回公司的路上。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:31.85,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,想着田山小姐在的话\N可以一起抽根烟。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:32.93,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,呃！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:36.69,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,对不起山田小姐\N我知道我不该在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:40.11,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我只是在占田山小姐的便宜！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:42.57,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,她没做错任何事！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.40,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,所以，那个……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:50.87,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,没关系的佐佐木先生\N我早就知道了。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:54.33,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,田山酱告诉我了。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:57.04,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哦，她说了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:07:59.79,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你们俩关系真好呢。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:03.80,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,Sa-slow-ki.。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:05.80,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(59,402)\shad2\bord2\c&H3E2CBE&\3c&H4DDFE4&\4c&H3D29BD&\pos(118,91.5)}Sa-slow-ki
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:05.55,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:07.63,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,是的，我们关系很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.05,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我就知道。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:12.30,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你们一定有很多共同点。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:17.81,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,都很细心体贴。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:23.65,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,啊对了，山田小姐。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:24.65,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:26.07,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,呃……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:29.57,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,田山小姐还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:33.58,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,她很好啊，怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:36.75,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,是投诉那件事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:43.34,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯，她跟我提了一点。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:46.09,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我担心她会不会有事。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:49.72,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,她没事。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:53.35,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我也担心过，\N但你知道她说了什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:56.43,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,吃碗拉面睡一觉就全忘了。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:00.60,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,是吗？那就好。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:06.15,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,希望她以后也能跟你倾诉。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:07.86,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,啊，不过……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:13.74,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,如果，她已经放下了\N我不该再提吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:18.25,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,不一定非得是这件事。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:23.75,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fs11\fnComic Sans MS\c&HFFFFFF&\frz-6.26\fax0.15\pos(168.5,98)}Cold
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:23.75,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\blur0.3\fs15\fnComic Sans MS\c&HFFFFFF&\frz-5.44\fax0.13\pos(312.5,112)}Cold
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:23.75,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs20\blur0.2\fnComic Sans MS\c&HFFFFFF&\fax0.12\pos(541,126)\frz355.9}Cold
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:23.17,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我会告诉她你很关心她。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:28.26,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,什么？你、你确定吗？\N我不会越界吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:32.01,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,越界？明明是她自己来找你谈的。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:34.26,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,现在说这个已经晚了。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:38.14,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哦，也是。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:41.89,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,对了，山田小姐。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:44.90,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,前几天谢谢你了。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:47.77,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我听田山小姐说了。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:52.90,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,她说你担心我情绪低落。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:59.08,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,一直没机会道谢\N不想在你工作的时候打扰你。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.08,0:10:00.54,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,哦，没事的。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:10.05,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,工作上的事让我很郁闷\N有人关心真的很感激。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:18.06,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,那就好，只要没越界……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:21.68,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,等等，越界？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:25.19,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我想现在说这个也已经晚了。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:29.82,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,那自然是顺理成章的结论了。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:35.95,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,啊，抱歉耽误你时间了。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:37.07,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,没关系。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:42.58,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我一直想像田山酱那样\N跟你聊聊天，今天能说上话真好。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:49.17,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,她现在不在\N不过你可以在这抽烟。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:51.09,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,谢谢。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:56.09,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,今天就算了。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:58.85,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不想让你沾上烟味。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:02.56,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,抱歉占用你的休息时间。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:04.02,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,再见。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:10.82,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,佐佐木先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:11.78,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:27.79,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,你头发上有片花瓣，一直都在。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.46,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,什么？一直？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.42,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,嗯。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:35.59,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,老头带着花……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:37.88,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,太可爱了。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.76,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我不忍心告诉你。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:41.30,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,抱歉。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:45.89,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不，呃，谢谢你。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:55.65,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,没想到山田小姐也会这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:59.07,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,她也有调皮的一面啊。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.68,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,佐佐木先生太迟钝了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:30.94,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,几乎有点好笑。
